products.title: Genesis Dark Grey Perfect Fit Roller Blind
products.description: Their genesis range comes in 6 colour variations and is the perfect choice for a modern look. This dark grey perfect fit roller blind is bang on trend and will add effortless style to any room in your home. The perfect fit aspect of this blind means it can clip straight on to pvc window frames - saving space and meaning no drills or screws.
